{"title":"黄山松——献给中国共产党","authors":["汪静之"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":6,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给中国共产党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪静之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山松！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挺立在高峰顶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气概万分雄壮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藐视千灾万难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽强地生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松根穿进岩石的缝隙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松根绕到岩石底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松根蟠结，好象长龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把陡峭的岩石捆绑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有庇护，没有依傍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在绝壁危峰的险境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你脚跟站稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊人的翠色一千尺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你饱吸千山万岭翠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展翅的雄姿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲霄的气势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比壮美！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不屈不挠的硬劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚忍刚强的韧性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么妩媚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难炼就骨如铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柢固根深不动摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你胸有波澜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮阔如东海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒发松涛象海涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山松！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你经过一千番冰雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一万次寒风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来是怒目视冰雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑傲对寒风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你傲雪凌霜不改翠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高撑翠色斗严冬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你受尽酷寒心愈烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝遍风刀气更雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰雪层层压不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒潮阵阵不曾凋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你性格刚强骨气硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节操忠贞格调高。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}